            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                    <h2>A Perfect Fit</h2>
                    <p>Glimpse works where you need it to, how you want it to. Insights are presented in digestable summaries, with the ability to drill down to tackle tough problems.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
